snippet.title: Genshin Impact - Wind, Courage and Wings (Amber Act 1)
snippet.description:
Watch live at https://www.twitch.tv/ayinmaiden (Sun to Wed 8/9pm EST) 

Wind, Courage and Wings (Amber Act 1)
Lepus Chapter: Act 1

►Objectives
0:00 Intro
0:08 1. Glide with the Wind
- Talk to Amber 

4:11 2. License to Glide
- Go to the exam point
- Talk to Amber
- Follow the route and fly to the finish line in time
- Talk to Amber 

7:33 3. Mondstadt Glider
- Go to the door of Mondstadt Cathedral
- Talk to Amber
- Follow the route and fly to the finish line in time
- Talk to Amber
- Follow the markers to arrive at the finish line in time
- Reach the doors of the Adventurers' Guild 

10:45 4. They Call Him Raptor
Track Raptor
- Look for clues to track Raptor (0/3)
- Investigate the strange sound up ahead
- Look for Raptor
- Look for the marks left by Raptor 

17:27 5. Outrider Style
- Enter Raptor's Hideout (The Reward for Courage is Flight)
- Defeat all enemies
- Hunt down Raptor
- Glide over the chasm
- Track down Raptor and arrest him!
- Talk to Amber
- Go to the Cathedral to get your gliding license
- Talk to Amber 

Details: https://genshin-impact.fandom.com/wiki/Wind,_Courage_and_Wings
